title: Cool.Edit.Pro.2.1_With_Custom_Patch_[LaMara8]
description:
This is the original Syntrillium Cool Edit Pro version 2.1

Unlike other installations I&#039;ve seen, in this version you only have to run the 2.1 install file and the patch and not go thru 2.0 -> REGISTER -> 2.1

I compiled the patch with the following registration info:

Name: ROR
Key: 200-00-3Z1XFL9C


Please post comments if anybody experiences registration problems, especially on Vista 64... If you are having problems with Vista 64, read the Vista64_fix.txt first.


Enjoy!
